50"], "resources": [{"files": 8, "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_elmo_ver02:data:sn85034082:00517177350:1907120501:0397/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn85034082/1907-12-05/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "rights": ["<p>The Library of Congress believes that the newspapers in Chronicling America are in the public domain or have no known copyright restrictions.  Newspapers published in the United States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.504336, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "sn85034082, 1907-12-05, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/gu", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["newspapers", "pickens county (ga.)", "cobb county (ga.)", "cobb", "marietta (ga.)", "cherokee county (ga.)", "marietta", "cobb county", "georgia", "paulding county (ga.)", "united states"], "subject_headings": ["Marietta (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Cobb County (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Paulding County (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Cherokee County (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Pickens County (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Georgia--Cobb County", "Georgia--Marietta", "United States--Georgia--Cobb--Marietta"], "subjects": [{"cherokee county (ga.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:cherokee+county+%28ga.%29&fo=json"}, {"cobb": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:cobb&fo=json"}, {"cobb county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:cobb+county&fo=json"}, {"cobb county (ga.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:cobb+county+%28ga.%29&fo=json"}, {"georgia": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:georgia&fo=json"}, {"marietta": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:marietta&fo=json"}, {"marietta (ga.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:marietta+%28ga.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"paulding county (ga.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:paulding+county+%28ga.%29&fo=json"}, {"pickens county (ga.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:pickens+county+%28ga.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-05-22T19:43:57.819Z", "title": "The Marietta journal (Marietta, Georgia;Marietta, Ga.), December 5, 1907", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn85034082/1907-12-05/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85034082/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn85034082", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/fe30c420-baf1-5614-b1d0-4789572ea47c"], "batch": ["gu_drteeth_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1866", "description": ["Weekly Began in 1866; ceased with: Vol. 43, no. 34 (Aug. 26, 1909). \"Official journal of the counties of Cobb, Paulding, Cherokee, and Pickens.\"--Vol. VI, no. 10 (March 15, 1872), page [2] \"Official journal of the counties of Cobb, Cherokee, and Pickens.\"--Vol. VIII, no. 33 (August 14, 1874), page [2] \"Official journal of the counties Cobb, and Pickens.\"--Vol. IX, no. 34 (August 20, 1875), page [2] \"Offiicial journal of the counties Cobb, Paulding, and Pickens.\"--Vol. XI, no. 44 (November 2, 1877), page [2] \"Official journal of the counties Cobb and Paulding.\"--Vol. XV, no. 37 (Sept 8, 1881), masthead. \"Official journal of the city and county.\"-- Vol. XVII, no. 10 (Mar. 1, 1883), masthead. \"Official journal of Marietta.\"--Vol. 43, no. 8 (Feb. 25, 1909), page [2] Some enumeration repeated and some apparently skipped; other irregularities in enumeration and chronology. Contains some extra issues. Merged with: Marietta courier, to form: Marietta journal and courier. Vol. II, no. 37 (September 18, 1868) (online surrogate); title from masthead (Georgia Historic Newspapers database, viewed April 5, 2023). Vol. 43, no. 34 (Aug. 26, 1909) (online surrogate); (Georgia Historic Newspapers database, viewed July 7, 2023). Marietta courier (DLC)sn 91099177 (OCoLC)24632189 Marietta journal and courier (DLC)sn 89053964 (OCoLC)21278095"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.512Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-15", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-15"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85034082/", "image_url": [], "index": 8, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [33.952304, -84.549051], "location": ["cobb", "paulding county", "cherokee county", "marietta", "cobb county", "georgia", "pickens county", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-84.549051, 33.952304], "number": ["2024-05-12t17:32:27.269094", "2996-0304", "1810", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85034082/1868-09-18/ed-1/", "univ of georgia", "online resource", "12402042", "sn89053964", "new york hist soc, newsp proj", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn85034082/1909-08-26/ed-1/", "sn91099177", "1", "microfilm service copy", "original", "2025-07-01t13:40:40.900000", "sn85034082", "univ of texas at austin", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["the marietta journal (marietta, georgia;marietta, ga.) 1866-1909", "catalog", "chronicling america", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 132.4039, "shelf_id": "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn85034082", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["newspapers", "pickens county (ga.)", "cobb county (ga.)", "cobb", "marietta (ga.)", "cherokee county (ga.)", "marietta", "cobb county", "georgia", "paulding county (ga.)", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:15:01.231Z", "title": "The Marietta journal", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn85034082/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271019/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1866", "dates": ["[1866 TO 1909]"], "description": ["Weekly Print began in 1866. Merged with: Marietta courier, to form: Marietta journal and courier. Vol. II No. 37 (September 18, 1868); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 16, 2024). Vol. 43, No. 34 (Aug. 26, 1909) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 16, 2024). Marietta courier Marietta journal and courier 2996-0436 (DLC) 2024271020 (OCoLC)1368027453"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:53.248Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271019/", "image_url": [], "index": 9, "language": ["english"], "location": ["cobb", "marietta", "cobb county", "georgia", "united states"], "number": ["2024271019", "online resource", "2996-0312", "1162048287", "2024271020", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["n